{
  "texts": [
    "To solve such confusion, we manually map such occasions to the correct language name.",
    "Despite our best efforts, there are rare situations in which the language is misclassified and we ask our vendor to skip such tasks during annotations.",
    "Finally, we stratified sample prompts based on the language.",
    "Proportions are primarily determined based on the number of prompts available for each language in the ShareGPT dataset (RyokoAI, 2023).",
    "This means that we allocate a higher proportion to commonly used languages such as Python and Chinese."
  ]
}